(4, 3, 'www.mtp.ie/home', 'Home', '- Ireland''s most accurate vehicle values', 'Home', 'Home', 'used car sales\r\ncar values\r\nused cars dublin\r\ncar prices\r\nBMW parts\r\nnew cars\r\nnew cars dublin\r\nnew car deals\r\nnew cars ireland\r\nused car dealerships dublin\r\nsell your car\r\n10 day car sales\r\n10 day SIMI figures\r\n20 day SIMI\r\n30 day SIMI\r\ncar price\r\neditorial\r\ncar news\r\nbuy a car\r\nsell a car\r\nselling my car\r\nhow much is my car\r\ncar ireland\r\n', '3', '39', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '96', '<pre><h6></h6><h2 style="font-family:helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: large; color: rgb(51, 153, 153); " class="&lt;img src= &lt;img src=" http:="" qbix-soft.pl="" mtp="" assets="" b406734b="" images="" pixel.gif"="" title="" rel="media06362804118543863" width="150" height="100">What you need to know....</span><br /></h2></pre><p style="font-family:helvetica, sans-serif;text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:medium">Motor Trade Publishers have been Ireland’s most prominent authority on used vehicle values since 1967. Our values are renowned for their accuracy and the depth to which we explore the used vehicle market is unrivaled. We provide reliable information to key areas of the motor industry with a stringent demand for timely and precise valuations. Our book of clients includes the vast majority of motor dealers, Revenue, Offices of the Financial Services&nbsp;Ombudsman, insurance companies, finance houses and other parties with a vested interest in receiving as close to definitive vehicle values as possible.</span><br /></p><h2 style="font-family:helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: large; color: rgb(51, 153, 153); " class="&lt;img src=" http:="" qbix-soft.pl="" mtp="" assets="" b406734b="" images="" pixel.gif"="" title="" rel="media9440845067147166" width="150" height="100">But don’t just take our word for it;</span></h2><div><span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:medium"><br /></span></div><span style="font-size:medium;font-family:helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-weight:bold">"The Car Sales Guide\r\nhas always been a valuable tool to be considered within our used car appraisal\r\nprocess"</span>. - &nbsp;<span style="font-style:italic">Cliff Veltom, Brand Manager, Audi Centre, Dublin</span></span><div><span style="font-style:italic;font-size:medium;font-family:helvetica, sans-serif" class="&lt;img src=" http:="" www.mtp.ie="" assets="" cb833906="" images="" pixel.gif"="" title="" rel="media13402790599502623" width="150" height="100"><br /></span></div><div><span style="font-family:helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-weight:bold">"The Car Sales Guide has played an instrumental role in the daily business and&nbsp;success of Motorpark. Without it, used vehicle</span><span style="font-weight:bold">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight:bold">values would be a guessing game". </span><span style="font-style:italic">- Gerard Halloran, General Manager, Motorpark</span></span></div><div><span style="font-size:medium;font-family:helvetica, sans-serif"><br /><br /></span>  </div>', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 'Home', 0),
