(91, 3, 'valuation', 'Valuation', 'Valuation', 'Valuation', 'Valuation', 'Valuation, vehicle price, price my car, how much is my car worth, car value, car price, car prices, cars value, car values, bmw price, audi price, citroen price, chevrolet price, alfa price, daihatsu price, fiat price, ford price, focus price, mondeo price, fiesta price, honda price, civic price, kia price, jaguar price, landrover price, lexus price, mercedes price, mazda price, mitsubishi price, mini price, nissan price, opel price, peugeot price, renault price, saab price, seat price, subaru price, suzuki price, toyota price, volswagen price, vw price, vw golf, vw passat, volvo price, used car sales\r\ncar values\r\nused cars dublin\r\ncar prices\r\nBMW parts\r\nnew cars\r\nnew cars dublin\r\nnew car deals\r\nnew cars ireland\r\nused car dealerships dublin\r\nsell your car\r\n10 day car sales\r\n10 day SIMI figures\r\n20 day SIMI\r\n30 day SIMI\r\ncar price\r\neditorial\r\ncar news\r\nbuy a car\r\nsell a car\r\nselling my car\r\nhow much is my car\r\ncar ireland\r\ncar valuation ireland\r\ntrade in value of car\r\ncar trade in value\r\ncar value ireland calculator', '4', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'index.php?r=site/valuation', NULL, '<span style="font-family:helvetica, sans-serif">*Note: The valuation provided pertains to the retail price from a motor dealer. It is not a trade in allowance value or asking price.</span>', NULL, 4, 1, 1, 'Valuation', 1),
